/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the cityscape. The sun shines brightly in the clear blue sky, casting a warm glow over the scene. Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, interspersed with trees that add a touch of green to the urban landscape. Power lines crisscross above, connecting the buildings and adding a sense of dynamism to the scene. The image is taken from a low angle, which emphasizes the height of the buildings and the expanse of the sky. The colors in the image are vibrant, with the blue of the sky contrasting beautifully with the green of the trees and the varied hues of the buildings.
